<h1>32 of the best websites</h1>
<h4>4<sup>th</sup> October 2007</h4>


	<p class="meta">Published in <a href="http://magazines.scholastic.co.uk/mag_issues/21825">Child Education PLUS November 2007</a></p>


<p class="author">By <b>Charlotte Ronalds</b> &#8212; Deputy Editor, <em>Child EDucation <span class="caps">PLUS</span></em></p>

<p class="intro">We at <em>ChildEd <span class="caps">PLUS</span></em> have been busy scouring the internet for the best websites to use in the <span class="caps">KS1</span> classroom. Here are the results&#8230;</p>

